# CODEOWNERS for Cotai

This file defines code ownership and review responsibilities for Cotai services and domains.
GitHub automatically requests reviews from listed owners on pull requests.

## Global Defaults

* @platform-team @infrastructure-team

## Service-Specific Ownership

# Auth Service — Authentication, OAuth2, JWT, MFA
/services/auth-service/ @auth-team @security-team

# Edital Service — Tender/RFQ management, publication, lifecycle
/services/edital-service/ @procurement-team

# Cotação Service — Quotation management, vendor responses, scoring
/services/cotacao-service/ @procurement-team @analytics-team

# Notificação Service — Email, SMS, in-app notifications
/services/notificacao-service/ @backend-team @platform-team

# Fornecedor Service — Vendor profiles, registration, evaluation
/services/fornecedor-service/ @procurement-team @vendor-management-team

# Extração Service — Document OCR, NLP, data extraction
/services/extracao-service/ @ml-team @data-team

# Estoque Service — Inventory management, stock levels, forecasting
/services/estoque-service/ @supply-chain-team

# Chat Service — Real-time messaging, collaboration
/services/chat-service/ @backend-team

