---

## Notes

- **@platform-team**: Infrastructure, deployment, observability, CI/CD
- **@auth-team**: Authentication, identity, security protocols
- **@security-team**: Security, compliance, secrets management
- **@procurement-team**: Core procurement domain (tenders, quotations, vendors)
- **@api-team**: API design, gRPC contracts, protocol buffers
- **@qa-team**: Testing, quality assurance, test automation
- **@backend-team**: Backend services, libraries, utilities

## Escalation

- **Security concerns**: Tag `@security-team` explicitly in comment
- **Architecture changes**: Create ADR and tag `@architecture-team`
- **Production incidents**: Ping on-call via PagerDuty (see `docs/runbooks/`)

